  "prompt": "How can I forget the past and focus on the future?",
  "response": "Here are some strategies to help you move forward:\n\n1. Acceptance\n- Acknowledge what happened\n- Understand you can't change the past\n- Practice self-forgiveness\n\n2. Mental Techniques\n- Practice mindfulness meditation\n- Use positive affirmations\n- Challenge negative thought patterns\n- Seek therapy if needed\n\n3. Practical Steps\n- Set new personal goals\n- Create a forward-looking plan\n- Develop new skills\n- Engage in activities you enjoy\n\n4. Emotional Management\n- Process past emotions\n- Let go of resentment\n- Practice gratitude\n- Focus on personal growth\n\n5. Lifestyle Changes\n- Surround yourself with supportive people\n- Limit contact with those who remind you of painful memories\n- Stay physically active\n- Maintain a healthy routine\n\n6. Professional Help\n- Consider counseling\n- Join support groups\n- Work with a life coach\n\n7. Perspective Shifts\n- View past experiences as learning opportunities\n- Recognize your resilience\n- Understand that everyone has challenges\n\nRemember that healing is a process. Be patient and kind to yourself as you work on moving forward.\n\nWould you like to discuss any specific aspects of moving past difficult experiences?",
